## Layout & Spacing Guidelines

### Consistent Spacing Scale
```css
/* Use consistent spacing throughout */
.section-padding-y { @apply py-16 md:py-24; }
.section-padding-x { @apply px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8; }
.container-max-width { @apply max-w-7xl mx-auto; }

/* Content spacing */
.content-spacing { @apply space-y-6 md:space-y-8; }
.grid-gap { @apply gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12; }
```

### Responsive Breakpoints
- Mobile: < 768px (single column)
- Tablet: 768px - 1023px (2 columns)
- Desktop: ≥ 1024px (3 columns where applicable)

### Typography Hierarchy
- H1: Hero headlines (text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl)
- H2: Section headers (text-3xl md:text-4xl)
- H3: Subsection headers (text-xl md:text-2xl)
- Body: Main text (text-base md:text-lg)
- Small: Supporting text (text-sm)

This structure ensures a cohesive, professional, and user-friendly landing page that effectively converts visitors into clients.